BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-09T22:45:00&endDate=2026-04-10T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Tuesday 7\, Wednesday 8 and Thursday 9 April\, after 2345 each evening\, no westbound service from Camden Road to Willesden Junction. The 2359 and 0015 services from Stratford will terminate at Camden Road. Use London Overground services from Euston to Willesden Junction\, Northern line from Camden Town\, or local bus routes 1\, 24\, 46 88 and 214 from Camden Road / Camden Town.
